  <h1>懂的入！不解释！</h1>
  <h5> <b class="red">186万</b>用户下载&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;推荐指数：<span class="red">★★★★★</span> </h5>
  <div class="botton_block">
    <button id="button1" class="button" onClick="location.href='${androidUrl}'">安卓下载</button>
    <button id="button2" class="button" onClick="location.href='itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=${iosUrl}'">苹果下载</button>
